    <h2>Artist: Ben Banker</h2>
  <p class="title">Gouache on 140 lb cold press paper</p>
  <p>2021 2022 2023</p>
  <p>Esteemed for his versatile artistry, Ben Banker unveils 'Dark Ninja', a 22" x 30" gouache opus, currently gracing a private collection in Florida. Crafted over three years, from 2021 to 2023, this work captures the essence of the artist's rich travels and life experiences. As a single father to four children, Banker's artistic expression is interwoven with his paternal journey, balancing the vivid chaos of creativity with the harmonious rhythm of family life. Each stroke is infused with the memories of landscapes traversed and the wisdom gained from a life lived fully on the move, from the solitude of national forests to the energy of urban landscapes.</p>

